headline: Gilead Sciences Stock Spikes After Q4 Results: Time to Buy?
summary: Biotech leader Gilead Sciences (GILD) made headlines on Wednesday, with its stock spiking nearly 6% after delivering favorable Q4 results yesterday evening.
